e [[新疆生产建设兵团|新疆生产建设兵团]] as [[Chinese_imperialism|Chinese imperialism]]. These tensions occasionally result in major incidents and violent clashes, such as [[Kazakh|Kazakh]] [[Exodus_from_Xinjiang|Exodus from Xinjiang]] in [[1962|1962]], in which 60,000 refugees fled into [[苏联|苏联]]; the [[Baren_Township_riot|Baren Township riot]] on [[April_5|April 5]], [[1990|1990]] that resulted in more than 50 deaths; the [[Ghulja_riot|Ghulja riot]] of [[February_5|February 5]], [[1997|1997]] that resulted in at least 9 deaths [http://www.hrw.org/backgrounder/asia/china-bck1017.htm]; and [[Urumqi_bus_bombs|Urumqi bus bombs]] of [[February_25|February 25]], [[1997|1997]] that killed 9 and injured 68.-->
